class-map match-all VOIP_SIG
 match ip dscp af31 
class-map match-any VOIP_RTP
 match ip dscp ef 
 match ip precedence 5 
!
policy-map VOIP
 class VOIP_SIG
  bandwidth remaining percent 1 
 class VOIP_RTP
  priority
